title: Umbrella Academy Number Five Vinyl Figure
body_html:
"I'm not doing this for money" Number Five has done the calculations and travelled forward (or backward?) to 2024 for their Youtooz debut! Standing at 4.6 inches tall with a red-handled fire axe swung over his shoulder casually and one hand resting in the pocket of his shorts, a stern look crosses his face with thin pursed lips as his short brown hair is swept over to the side with its fringe curling down onto his forehead. Always looking smart, he wears a dark blue blazer over a black, red and white argyle vest along with a white shirt and tie, while his long black socks feed into laced dress shoes. The exterior of his packaging sees Number 5 standing on a wooden desk after laying waste to a room full of people. The interior of his packaging is a stark black covered in red and white flying bullets, knives, umbrellas and crosshairs which continues onto the protective sleeve where his figure can be seen through the large clear window at the packaging's front.

  • Height 4.6"
  • This collectible ships in a matte, embossed, protective outer sleeve and a custom sized plastic protector for maximum protection during shipping
